data.description: Discover luxury living in this 4 bed/3 bath (4th room currently used as a office) within the gated Colony Ridge Subdivision Phase I. Professionally painted cabinets in kitchen and throughout the entire home to include bathrooms and laundry room. While LVP graces the foyer, LR (just installed Nov 2023) laundry and flex space. Enjoy your flex room w/ pocket doors, new paint in every room, new carpet 2021, new lighting throughout and kitchen island w/granite countertop. Dive into the 47ft inground saltwater pool with a brand-new pool liner 2022, screened back porch, front porch, 2 car garage, and a brand new 6ft privacy fence offer both style and privacy. 300 ft deep water well + sprinkler system, front & back irrigation + manibloc plumbing system. New roof just installed This property includes brand new 6ft privacy fence, with a 300ft deep water well that not only provides water for front and back irrigation but also provides water for the pool, which helps in keeping water bill low. bonus- Alarm system and surround sound speakers on property. Call today to tour this beautiful property !
